metadata.description:
Beyond the physical form lies a powerful notion,  
An idea that endures with steadfast devotion,  
For concepts are impervious to mortal attacks,  
Indomitable, they persist and always bounce back. 
-CultDAO

A token of appreciation for the CultDAO members and investee partners who participate in ETH DENVER 2023
